  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>\"Hush, little baby, don't say a word / Momma's gonna kill for you the whole damn world.\"</em></p><h5 id=\"benefit\">Benefit</h5><p>You tend to go above and beyond when it comes to finishing off your enemies. Twice per long rest, you may spend your bonus action to max the damage of your next attack or jutsu that would target a bloodied creature. You also gain the ability to use your reaction when you would successfully attack a bloodied creature to force them to make a Flat saving throw with a DC of 10 or gain the dazed condition</p>",
